{{expand|time=2013-06-07T18:26:56+00:00}}
{{refimprove|time=2013-06-07T18:26:56+00:00}}
《'''完美'''》是一部[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]都市情感[[連續劇|連續劇]]，共26集，由[[北京君为文化传播有限公司|北京君为文化传播有限公司]]出品，导演为[[张建栋|张建栋]]<ref>{{cite news|title=賀歲劇《完美》開播　袁泉王學兵邊吵邊愛|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/5/2/13/n810646.htm|accessdate=2013-06-07|newspaper=大紀元|date=2005-02-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114318/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/5/2/13/n810646.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=王學兵袁泉"吵出愛情" 張建棟拍"完美"避審查|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2005-02/01/content_2533236.htm|accessdate=2013-06-07|newspaper=北京青年報|date=2005-02-01|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305062601/http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2005-02/01/content_2533236.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，编剧为[[吴海燕|吴海燕]]，於2005年播出<ref>{{cite news|title=袁泉王學兵春節攜手熒屏 袁泉：完美只在瞬間|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/5/2/1/n799991.htm|accessdate=2013-06-07|newspaper=大紀元|date=2005-02-01|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120252/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/5/2/1/n799991.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

故事围绕着律师佟言（[[王学兵|王学兵]]）与设计师白璇（[[袁泉|袁泉]]）之间的爱情<ref>{{cite news|title=王學兵、袁泉等人到場 《完美》央視開演|url=http://big5.china.com.cn/chinese/CU-c/774001.htm|accessdate=2013-06-07|newspaper=北京青年報|date=2005-01-31|archive-date=2015-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150519030409/http://big5.china.com.cn/chinese/CU-c/774001.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="southcn">{{cite news|author=任嫣|title=王學兵、袁泉《完美》中苦戀|url=http://www.southcn.com/ent/celeb/yuanquan/gallery/200412091534.htm|accessdate=2013-06-07|newspaper=南方網|date=2003-12-02|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305002713/http://www.southcn.com/ent/celeb/yuanquan/gallery/200412091534.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，期间又穿插着陶殊磊（[[张博|张博]]）与陈子欢（[[孙菲菲|孙菲菲]]）之间的爱情。

有分离有重合，但始终充满着爱。

